{"tid":844971,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[FPS]programming 分享區","createTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T04:04:42.000Z","uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9932622bf65344d38875a2f4667041be774696","tid":844971,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"我仲未搵倒一間有提供FPS收付款API既銀行<br />\n如果有收款通知, 舖仔就可以完全唔用任何 payment gateway 直接用戶口收錢<br />\npaypal 係香港可以馬上收皮, 4%袋足咁多年咁爽呀啦<br />\n<br />\n現時只係諗倒 FPS收倒錢後, 收倒訊息埋電郵 就自動當完成 payment<br />\n仲有冇人諗倒其他方法<br />\n<br />\n歡迎鳩流鳩流一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f38629df5e8f139cd22192400dc2c09fc7c99d","tid":844971,"uid":155997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"香港銀行有出 Merchant service, 未知詳情。<br />\n（唔知點解一睇到FPS 就諗起 Frame per second<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"39a52372937842ca28380127ad0b5322343a435e","tid":844971,"uid":110163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔係話遲d有開放 API 咩"},{"pid":"ed347e4a810661b53e38b9f8d6ff7cd6cdfd4441","tid":844971,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"39a52372937842ca28380127ad0b5322343a435e","tid":844971,"uid":110163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔係話遲d有開放 API 咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇反，起碼要第四步先睇倒，依家仲係第一步查下有咩product廢功能<br />\n<br />\n歐盟已經立左法強制銀行出api<br />\n但香港都係自願參加，進度好慢<br />\n銀聯話就黎出，但唔知收費點<br />\n<br />\n大家準備進入，用咩銀行都冇咩分別既年代啦<br />\n<br />\n有得自己寫api，對網上交易好有用<br />\n<br />\nfps其實已經做到，找換店網上化，對人仔反大陸唔洗去舖，直接同找換店網上交易，去機禁出黎就得<br />\n等緊出埋 jpy usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ec6917fb34435ff20097d668a1dbdcdf8f874c","tid":844971,"uid":2341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"用citibank既話用佢套API點睇? citibank好似有API比你查transaction<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77a98d161cf3d417903f40e05463024115517a2","tid":844971,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ec6917fb34435ff20097d668a1dbdcdf8f874c","tid":844971,"uid":2341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"用citibank既話用佢套API點睇? citibank好似有API比你查transaction<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"citi bank好似最齊功能<br />\n其實可以，但睇下佢可唔可以落倒remark係一條record到<br />\n如果唔得就要收小幾豪子，用隨機小數位對數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89f5d3bdb23352fd23df764933d28e7d83742de","tid":844971,"uid":114269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a52372937842ca28380127ad0b5322343a435e","tid":844971,"uid":110163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔係話遲d有開放 API 咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"FPS個phase應該去到出年年中"},{"pid":"1b2d27b849856ffe93d72ad050ee51849d59986b","tid":844971,"uid":105173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"公司明明未登記, 但今日就收到第一筆FPS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知想點, 又無API, 又無人講點用, 淨得廣告。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df181b23eb56ba1781359f7ba774d83fc5376b36","tid":844971,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b2d27b849856ffe93d72ad050ee51849d59986b","tid":844971,"uid":105173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"公司明明未登記, 但今日就收到第一筆FPS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces